parameters.body:
If you wish to add or remove poles to or from this project, advance the status to "Remove or Add Poles."  When you do so, you will receive instructions on how to remove and add poles.
If you do not wish to make edits to this project, advance the project status to "No Route Changes, Attaching."
Note: Any update to this project is subject to evaluation by PNM personnel, and may require eventual submission of a new project.
parameters.subject: Route Re Evaluation

parameters.body:
To remove poles from this project, load the project in map view, set the project as "active," and select Remove Stations from the Action dropdown. Select the stations to be removed, and click Selected Stations.
To add poles to this project, load the project in map view, set the project as "active," select the stations you wish to add to the project, select Add Stations in the Action dropdown, and click Selected Stations.
When completed, advance the project status.
parameters.subject: Editing Your Project
